{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://docs.inspireui.com","title":"InspireUI Document","description":"InspireUI document"}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Multi Language","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"BeoNews Pro - React Native mobile app for Wordpress","meta_description":"BeoNews is an app that does magic for your website by converting your Wordpress website into mobile true native app with customized contents within a fillip.","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"beonews","toc":null,"keywords":["beonews","beonews pro magento","wordpress app","react-native","react-native app"]},"html":"<h2 id=\"change-the-default-languages\"><a href=\"#change-the-default-languages\" aria-label=\"change the default languages permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Change the default Languages</h2>\n<p>Open <strong>src/common/Languages.js</strong> and edit the default language for the app at the bottom up the page</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">  let Language = Languages[&#39;en&#39;];</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"change-the-language-to-rtl-right-to-left\"><a href=\"#change-the-language-to-rtl-right-to-left\" aria-label=\"change the language to rtl right to left permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Change the language to RTL (right to left)</h4>\n<p>Open <strong>src/common/Constants.js</strong> and edit the default option to <strong>RTL: true</strong> </p>\n<p>On ios you need to change the plist like this screenshot:</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b8ebdada719b34b3aed01eb400ea37f0/91993/beonew-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 53.10846560846561%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"beonew 2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b8ebdada719b34b3aed01eb400ea37f0/efcfb/beonew-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b8ebdada719b34b3aed01eb400ea37f0/11053/beonew-2.png 200w,\n/static/b8ebdada719b34b3aed01eb400ea37f0/1b42c/beonew-2.png 400w,\n/static/b8ebdada719b34b3aed01eb400ea37f0/efcfb/beonew-2.png 800w,\n/static/b8ebdada719b34b3aed01eb400ea37f0/d25cb/beonew-2.png 1200w,\n/static/b8ebdada719b34b3aed01eb400ea37f0/22e61/beonew-2.png 1600w,\n/static/b8ebdada719b34b3aed01eb400ea37f0/4b363/beonew-2.png 2400w,\n/static/b8ebdada719b34b3aed01eb400ea37f0/91993/beonew-2.png 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>Config Xcode to support RTL as default</p>\n<p>To add more font, you can able to add to the collection from \"<strong>Fonts provided by application</strong>\" (see above screenshot)</p>","fields":{"slug":"/beonews/multi-language/"},"timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"Change the default Languages Open  src/common/Languages.js  and edit the default language for the app at the bottom up the page Change theâ€¦","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/minh/Data/Projects/web/inspireui-document/content/beonews/multi-language.md"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/beonews/multi-language/"}}